```pulse
fn ref_apply (#a #b:Type) (r:ref (a -> b)) (x:a) (#f:erased (a -> b))
  requires pts_to r f
  returns y:b
  ensures pts_to r f ** pure (y == (reveal f) x)
{
  let f = !r;
  f x
}
```

